  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 63-11-30, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE THE NONADJUDICATION OR EXPUNCTION OF CERTAIN OFFENSES UNDER THIS SECTION FOR THE HOLDER OF A COMMERCIAL DRIVER'S LICENSE OR COMMERCIAL LEARNING PERMIT WHO WAS NOT OPERATING A VEHICLE THAT REQUIRED THE POSSESSION OF SUCH A LICENSE OR PERMIT AT THE TIME OF THE OFFENSE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
